  "keyFeatures": [
    "Hardened Linux OS optimized for AI agent execution",
    "Pre-configured mixtapes with popular AI coding agents (OpenCode, Claude Code, Gemini CLI)",
    "Multi-format image builds (Raw EFI, QCOW2, kernel artifacts)",
    "Isolated agent environment with restricted shell and package access",
    "Dual-daemon architecture (stereosd system daemon, agentd agent manager)",
    "gVisor sandbox support for enhanced security isolation",
    "NixOS-based declarative configuration with flake support",
    "Sub-3-second boot time optimization"
  ],
